com.ihealth.communication.contol

Interface AmProfile


  • public interface AmProfile
    Public APIs for the AM serials device profiles

    Clients need to calliHealthDevicesManager#registerClient register. When new data from AM device, The CallbackiHealthDevicesCallback#onDeviceNotify can be triggered should call.
